{
  "texts": [
    "In the first scenario, participants see a cue word and an image segment.",
    "They have to classify the segment by indicating whether it matches the word (Müller, Thoß, et al., 2024).",
    "In the second scenario, participants see an AI prediction and an image.",
    "They have to indicate whether they accept or reject the AI prediction (Maehigashi et al., 2023a).",
    "Despite being structurally identical, the former scenario was classified as image-focused and the latter as AI-focused."
  ]
}